    <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
        <body>
            <div xml:id="KT378-kilavi">
                <p type="edition">makaṭ pōkkiya cevili teyvattiṟkup parāyatu. </p>


                <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">The deity entreated by the foster-mother, who
                    had let [her] daughter go. </p>
            </div>

            <div xml:id="KT378">
                <lg type="edition">
                    <l> ñāyiṟu kāyātu maraniḻaṟ paṭṭu</l>
                    <l> malaimutaṟ ciṟuneṟi maṇaṉmikat tāayt</l>
                    <l> taṇmaḻai talaiyiṉ ṟāka nannīttuc</l>
                    <l> cuṭarvāy neṭuvēṟ kāḷaiyoṭu</l>
                    <l> maṭamā varivai pōkiya curaṉē.</l>


                </lg>

                <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                    <l> That today it be a place of cool rain</l>
                    <l> [and] sand spread much on the small paths on the mountain</l>
                    <l> [and] shade fall from a tree without the sun being hot</l>
                    <l> – the desert, where the inexperienced dark young woman has gone</l>
                    <l rend="indent"> with the young man [bearing] a long spear with glowing mouth ,</l>
                    <l rend="indent8"> after she left us.</l>


                </lg>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
